Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.83,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's smartphone?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I need you to find her location.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one second.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.38,0:00:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried accessing the GSC's central network,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't identify her location.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.27,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can find at least some clue...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.98,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.63,0:00:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.43,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...? Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? {uwu?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.83,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the note said this floor...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.35,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I had been hoping for an opportunity to \Nhave a talk with you like this, face to face.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher in charge of the \NFederal Investigations Club SCHALE,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.20,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that mysterious organization \Ninvoked by the GSC President.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be alarmed. {BE NOT AFRAID}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no intention of becoming your enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the opposite, in fact.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.48,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't care less about what happens \Nto such an insignificant school as Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, on the other hand... \NYou're different.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider you an extremely potent threat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.98,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, where are my manners? \NI haven't introduced myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.09,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Why don't we call me... Black Suit?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rather fond of this name, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We are just like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We also hail from outside of Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.87,0:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've simply occupied a different realm from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gematria.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our name.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it in terms you would be familiar with,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.94,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it is an organization, of which I am a member.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.07,0:05:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gematria's mission is in observation, \Nexploration, and experimentation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.26,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From that perspective, you may think of us \Nas an undefined existence, similar to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.07,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, if I might be so bold...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I interest you in working together with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You would turn down this opportunity \Nto glimpse mystical truths?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.49,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}do{\i0} you seek here in Kivotos?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to get Hoshino back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.45,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And what exactly gives you \Nthe authority to make this demand?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.67,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hoshino is no longer a student of Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you've been reading the \Nforms your students give you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw the withdrawal form that she left.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more that you can do, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Comment: 10,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't signed that form yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hoshino's still part of the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still the vice president of Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's still one of my precious students.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you are their teacher,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.99,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,anything your students do requires your signature.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an inconvenient concept.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the ones who \Ndeceived my students, all of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.48,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You toyed with their feelings \Nand took advantage of their pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.92,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to classify our actions as "good" or "evil", \NI'm sure they would fall into the latter category.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are still within the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a distinction I must insist on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.67,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the disaster that struck \NAbydos was not our doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.06,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sandstorm that engulfed Abydos \Nwas extremely rare, yes.
Comment: 10,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But like any natural phenomenon, \Nit could have happened at any time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.83,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But like any natural phenomenon, \Nit could have happened at any time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The people may suffer from thirst as a result.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that happens, those looking \Nto sell water are bound to appear.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply the natural course of events.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.49,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that water is sold at an exorbitant price?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly a rare occurrence.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Such scenarios are commonplace in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.84,0:07:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that have exploit those that have not.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak have no right to choose their own future.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.18,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could simply give up on Hoshino, \NI can offer protection for Abydos in exchange.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.56,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be theirs again. A life where \Nthey can go to school without fear.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what Hoshino would want, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that were true, those girls wouldn't want this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So no matter what I say, \Nyou insist on opposing us.
Comment: 10,0:07:59.35,0:08:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are powerless. You lack any means of fighting us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are powerless.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack any means of fighting us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's someone who needs \Nmy help, I'll stand and fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds don't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.53,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to prove to them that their voices will \Nreach someone as long as they keep trying.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are those girls still alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, their voices reached me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just walk away?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their problem. It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why why why why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.51,0:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Why do you refuse?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.02,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This entire time, those girls were in pain, \Nand not a single adult took responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying you'll take responsibility?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even their family. Why should you?
Comment: 10,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Comment: 10,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not their family.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm not their family.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be there,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just happened to meet them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I am to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Children are crying for help!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What more reason do you need?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.51,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it means for an adult \Nto take responsibility in your eyes?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If the children laugh, you laugh with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're sad, you stay by their side.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're lost, you show them the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be an adult!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't be more mistaken.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults shape society to their own will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.75,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They decide what is right, what is proper.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is normal and what is not.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The powerful dominate the lowly.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The educated rule the ignorant.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong devour the weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be an adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.34,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have held dominion over all of Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been yours. The authority, the privileges...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the Mystics that fill this academy city.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.40,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been for a brief moment, \Nbut you held it all in the palm of your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you let it all go without a second thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth and mystery. Authority. Money. Power.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To throw it all away is nonsense. Meaningless.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I told you, I'm sure you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there is no point in talking further.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I had such high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's truly a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.46,0:10:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find Miss Hoshino in the laboratory \Nbeneath Kaiser PMC's desert base.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.39,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With Mimesis, we had observed the reverse of Mystic - in other words, Terror.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.43,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We were interested in whether it \Ncould be applied to a living student.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.71,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She was supposed to be a \Ntest bed for confirming our theories.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your theories?
Comment: 10,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that negotiations have failed,
Comment: 10,0:11:12.78,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there is naught I can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.69,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that negotiations have failed, \Nthere is naught I can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is regrettable, but our involvement ends here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So then Hoshino...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, take her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.35,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is no longer any concern of ours.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.12,0:11:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is assuming that director \Nwill allow you to reach her in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we were able to have this talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May we meet again, somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A laboratory under the Kaiser PMC base...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they've been holding her captive...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go save her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't be hasty.
Comment: 10,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Comment: 10,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what do we even say to Hoshino when we find her?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.14,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do we even \Nsay to Hoshino when we find her?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, more importantly,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to scold her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back on her own word.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be punished.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll scold her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For her sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.71,0:12:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all meet her together and say, "welcome home."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Where did that corny line come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too romantic!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It just screams blue skies and shiny memories! {Need... blue archive... pun... Tried looking at the OST names for inspiration but idk how well it works --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could pull that off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you won't, Serika.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll say it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it is a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.47,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't catch me dead saying that!
Comment: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nonomi laugh}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but there's only five of us -
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't win with just us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we need to find some allies.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.06,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about PS68?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they did help us before, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone. It's been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well, Hifumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all thanks to your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.54,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to go visit you at your school, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have certainly changed since we last met.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.41,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wish we'd known sooner \Nwhat Hoshino was going through.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could have stopped her.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we just couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.09,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean you're here about Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, about that...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.14,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like Trinity to help us save Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try asking the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.36,0:14:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask for your help, Miss Nagisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should I eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.59,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This shortcake is bursting with cream \Nand pairs beautifully with the tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But this mont blanc is hard to pass up as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Miss Nagisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.83,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The students of Abydos have helped me in the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So please -
Comment: 10,0:14:39.39,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This company, Kaiser PMC,
Comment: 10,0:14:43.08,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly seems like \Nit would be a bad influence on our students.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.39,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This company, Kaiser PMC, certainly seems like \Nit would be a bad influence on our students.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll hel-
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have that treaty to worry about as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot afford to act carelessly.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I have some time to consider?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So no answer yet, huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this was my idea...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like finding help is going \Nto be harder than we thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.36,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine this next group will help us, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.46,0:15:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we can't give up.
Comment: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Serika noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.39,0:15:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.62,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that the others couldn't attend this meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have liked Chinatsu to be here, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.85,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But this school has a bit of trouble following the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... for being late.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but, that's... mine...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for keeping you waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We just managed to finish up -
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your break!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's trouble in the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the tea!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the confusion!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are things always like this around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's actually a bit on the quiet side.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.99,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I wonder how \Nthe talks are going on their end?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Head Prefect is busy at the moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not available to meet right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bow down and lick my feet -
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.33,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you have zero pride as an adult? \NWouldn't you normally hesitate at least?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such clear eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get off of me already!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him. He's on his knees.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation must be quite serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, President Hina...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.67,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not actually kneeling, he's... um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking... my feet...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Prefect Team didn't give us an answer, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We did what we could! {Well, HE did what he could... the glorious bastard...}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.78,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones left are Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But will they agree to help us...?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.47,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This one's the one.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.95,0:17:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what gives?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.36,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the address they gave me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.06,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? You're telling me this is the PS68 office?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was a miscommunication?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.49,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This was our only lead on where to find them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, we came all this way for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, just where did they disappear off to?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss, been a while!
Comment: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome in!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful stall!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost feels nostalgic, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiba Seki Ramen actually started out of a stall, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like I'm back in those days, almost.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can eat your ramen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I don't know what would've \Nhappened if it weren't for that money.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you would have kept on anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like quitting was a choice anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.78,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still plenty of people out there \Nwho're waiting to eat my ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These two adorable girls showed up earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They looked right happy eating, said my \Nramen was just the thing after a tiring day.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't ask for more than that.
Comment: 10,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{He~}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How're things for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, not great...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried asking different people for help, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.51,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's one group \Nwe haven't been able to find.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't find them, I guess we just have to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, can we get the cheque?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.57,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to fight Kaiser PMC for free?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.16,0:19:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what that does for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, and I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.89,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kayoko, take a closer look.
Comment: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.05,0:19:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"We don't need payment. Being able \Nto eat this ramen is enough for us."
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this face says, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Yes, that's just how brave Miss Aru is!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.75,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't waste time with words as \Nshe marches into hell for a bowl of ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the picture of hard-boiled!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I think it over first?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.07,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Aru?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, hold on, Aru!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't beat yourself up over it, Sensei -
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith that they'll come help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.69,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, my restaurant will always be here \Nas long as the customers believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same idea in the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.33,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything goes wrong, \Njust start over and try again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.59,0:21:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll always be a path forward, \Nas long as you believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.81,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you're done...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.46,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you come back \Nfor a bowl of delicious ramen!
Comment: 10,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Alt timings for a rewrite}
Comment: 10,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Alt timings for a rewrite}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Comment: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nn} 
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to go whenever.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've packed plenty of ammunition.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.18,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser PMC doesn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the information Sensei gave us,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.67,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino is being held in District 51, \Ninside the Kaiser PMC base.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Our objective is to rescue Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.55,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{=5}Let's do this.

